There are two possible ways to do this:

1. If you have activity access then move the activity to the back.

        activity.moveTaskToBack(false);

[From Official Documentation][1]

&gt; Move the task containing this activity to the back of the activity
&gt; stack. The activity&#39;s order within the task is unchanged.

2. You can restore the activity to the front

        Intent intent = new Intent(PipScreenActivity.this, PipScreenActivity.class);
        intent.setFlags(Intent.FLAG_ACTIVITY_REORDER_TO_FRONT);
        activity.startActivity(intent);


  [1]: https://developer.android.com/reference/android/app/Activity.html#moveTaskToBack(boolean)

